dataset_id: GRACE ATMOSPHERE AND OCEAN DE-ALIASING GFZ RELEASE 6.0
title: GRACE ATMOSPHERE AND OCEAN DE-ALIASING GFZ RELEASE 6.0
summary: The GRACE Atmosphere and Ocean De-aliasing dataset contains spherical harmonic coefficients of combined barotropic or baroclinic sea level and vertical integrated pressure variations at 6-hour sample rate.  It is used as a correction product for the Level 2 GRACE datasets.
